room_title: Escape room "Z0d1ack K1773r" by Bakersfield Breakout Zone in Bakersfield
room_description:
You have gotten a lead where an active serial killer is, you want to confirm this lead. But now you are stuck in the middle of his trap.
As you are running through the forest, you stumble upon what seems to be an old forgotten cabin... Once inside you realize you have made a mistake... Can you escape or will you become a number?
